#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/doc/webgpu-compute-api-user.md:1
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/doc/webgpu-compute-api-user.md:3
msgid ""
"The new WebGPU compute API allows offloading computations from the CPU to "
"the GPU using WebGPU compute shaders through the new `vtkWebGPUComputePass` "
"and `vtkWebGPUComputePipeline` classes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/doc/webgpu-compute-api-user.md:6
msgid ""
"A `vtkWebGPUComputePass` is used to set the inputs and outputs to the "
"compute shader, execute it and get the results back to the CPU. A "
"`vtkWebGPUComputePipeline` contains one or more `vtkWebGPUComputePass` that "
"can be executed one after the other in a single `vtkWebGPUComputePipeline-"
">Dispatch()` call."
msgstr ""

